{"tid":740018,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老R波踢]祖雲主席談C朗轉會：他做主動","createTime":"2018-07-12T13:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T14:00:21.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"624336d2002073a9bde802fde1abed05c57a3022","tid":740018,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度轉投祖雲達斯一事轟動球壇，球會主席Giuseppe Marotta直言對獲球王級人馬來投十分開心，並指對方才是整宗交易的主導者，「老婦人」不過是把握了這個難得的好機會。<br />\n<br />\nC朗以1億歐元身價轉戰意甲，將成為祖雲達斯再次挑戰歐聯冠軍的利器。對於獲得頂級鋒將加盟，老婦人主席Giuseppe Marotta自然開心，而他更大爆是C朗本人主導是次轉會：「我很開心，非常開心。這件事是由C朗本人推動，他選擇了祖雲。當我們知道有機會得到他，我們球會上下也同意並盡最大可能將他帶到都靈。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自C朗轉會的消息轉出後，不少球壇名宿都祝福這名葡萄牙球星，其中球王比利亦盛讚對方作了一個英明決定。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=DzdwbEpQRAjKQMNLbQ1E9KMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=d3aafe01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"122da7ee8d7197d561ab7d5cb2c97d5bccd3b7bb","tid":740018,"uid":28850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"比利盛讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1c5b03928227d91099cf875d10161606465d47","tid":740018,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122da7ee8d7197d561ab7d5cb2c97d5bccd3b7bb","tid":740018,"uid":28850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"比利盛讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}